      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about hotlines and stuff but they dont actually change anything. they just listen and then i'm still stuck in this life. it feels like the more i try to fight it, the worse it gets. like the world is just this huge, loud place that wants me to fail and i'm just tired of fighting a battle i can't win. everything just feels so heavy and permanent.",
